00:32:15.460 --> 00:32:19.260
but are concerned about
things like your kids

00:32:19.260 --> 00:32:22.830
getting taken by CPS as happened
to that couple in Maryland?

00:32:22.830 --> 00:32:23.580
SARA ZASKE: Right.

00:32:23.580 --> 00:32:24.190
Absolutely.

00:32:24.190 --> 00:32:26.580
I mean, we do have that problem.

00:32:26.580 --> 00:32:28.950
Germans have a sense of
community in the sense

00:32:28.950 --> 00:32:31.170
that, if their kids
gets in trouble

00:32:31.170 --> 00:32:32.430
that people will help them.

00:32:32.430 --> 00:32:35.610
And here we've come
to a part of society

00:32:35.610 --> 00:32:39.750
where people tend to
call the police on you.

00:32:39.750 --> 00:32:41.340
The best advice
