could you look out your window,

00:32:57.155 --> 00:32:58.830
make sure they're OK?

00:32:58.830 --> 00:33:01.080
I think if we start
to draw people in

00:33:01.080 --> 00:33:05.250
to be proactively helpful
instead of negative,

00:33:05.250 --> 00:33:07.546
then perhaps we can
start to build that here.

00:33:07.546 --> 00:33:08.379
AUDIENCE: Thank you.

00:33:08.379 --> 00:33:09.420
SARA ZASKE: Your welcome.

